 politischen Engagements im Ruhestand neu.  aSocial activism in old age: in light of the generation of '68 reaching retirement age, the question of the forms of political engagement in retirement are being raised anew.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCivil societyzGermany. 0aOlder peoplexPolitical activityzGermany. 0aRetireesxPolitical activityzGermany. 4a68er. 4aBürgerschaftliches Engagement. 4aDemografischer Wandel. 4aDiskurs. 4aPolitik. 4aPolitikwissenschaft. 4aPolitische Soziologie. 4aSozialstaat. 4aSoziologie. 4aZivilgesellschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gerontology.2bisacsh  aCivil Society.  aDemographic Change.  aDiscourse.  aPolitical Science.  aPolitical Sociology.  aPolitics.  aSociology.  aVolunteering.  aWelfare State.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2016z9783110485332oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070101208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839433065zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839433065423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839433065/original  a978-3-11-070100-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  a978-3-11-070101-2  PP Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DSWb2016  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016